5.2 Processing a Guess
======================

The first part of the guessing game program will ask for user input,
process that input, and check that the input is in the expected form.
To start, we'll allow the player to input a guess.  Enter the code in
Listing 2-1 into ‚Äòsrc/main.rs‚Äô.

use std::io;

fn main() {
    println!("Guess the number!");

    println!("Please input your guess.");

    let mut guess = String::new();

