In the ‚ÄòCargo.toml‚Äô file, everything that follows a header is part of
that section that continues until another section starts.  In
‚Äò[dependencies]‚Äô you tell Cargo which external crates your project
depends on and which versions of those crates you require.  In this
case, we specify the ‚Äòrand‚Äô crate with the semantic version specifier
‚Äò0.8.5‚Äô.  Cargo understands Semantic Versioning (http://semver.org)
