‚Äòtrue‚Äô, and the ‚Äòsign_in_count‚Äô gets a value of ‚Äò1‚Äô.

fn build_user(email: String, username: String) -> User {
    User {
        active: true,
        username: username,
        email: email,
        sign_in_count: 1,
    }
}

