than ‚Äòderive‚Äô; for more information, see the ‚ÄúAttributes‚Äù section of the
Rust Reference
(https://doc.rust-lang.org/book/../reference/attributes.html).

Our ‚Äòarea‚Äô function is very specific: it only computes the area of
