that ‚ÄòOk‚Äô is wrapping.  However, if the value is an ‚ÄòErr‚Äô value, this
method calls the code in the ‚Äòclosure‚Äô, which is an anonymous function
we define and pass as an argument to ‚Äòunwrap_or_else‚Äô.  We'll cover
