      Adding `adder` as member of workspace at `file:///projects/add`

Running ‚Äòcargo new‚Äô inside a workspace also automatically adds the newly
created package to the ‚Äòmembers‚Äô key in the ‚Äò[workspace]‚Äô definition in
the workspace ‚ÄòCargo.toml‚Äô, like this:

[workspace]
resolver = "2"
members = ["adder"]

At this point, we can build the workspace by running ‚Äòcargo build‚Äô.  The
files in your ‚Äòadd‚Äô directory should look like this:

‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Cargo.lock
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Cargo.toml
‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ adder
‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Cargo.toml
