to force a value to be dropped before the end of its scope.

If we try to call the ‚ÄòDrop‚Äô trait's ‚Äòdrop‚Äô method manually by modifying
the ‚Äòmain‚Äô function from Listing 15-14, as shown in Listing 15-15, we'll
