impl List {
    fn tail(&self) -> Option<&RefCell<Rc<List>>> {
        match self {
            Cons(_, item) => Some(item),
            Nil => None,
        }
    }
}

fn main() {}

We're using another variation of the ‚ÄòList‚Äô definition from Listing
15-5.  The second element in the ‚ÄòCons‚Äô variant is now
