modify the ‚Äòi32‚Äô value as we did in Listing 15-24, we want to modify the
‚ÄòList‚Äô value a ‚ÄòCons‚Äô variant is pointing to.  We're also adding a
‚Äòtail‚Äô method to make it convenient for us to access the second item if
we have a ‚ÄòCons‚Äô variant.

In Listing 15-26, we're adding a ‚Äòmain‚Äô function that uses the
definitions in Listing 15-25.  This code creates a list in ‚Äòa‚Äô and a
