count is 1, not 0.  Then Rust drops ‚Äòa‚Äô, which decreases the reference
count of the ‚Äòa‚Äô ‚ÄòRc<List>‚Äô instance from 2 to 1 as well.  This
instance's memory can't be dropped either, because the other ‚ÄòRc<List>‚Äô
