We can fix the problem of the spawned thread not running or ending
prematurely by saving the return value of ‚Äòthread::spawn‚Äô in a variable.
The return type of ‚Äòthread::spawn‚Äô is ‚ÄòJoinHandle‚Äô.  A ‚ÄòJoinHandle‚Äô is
