We also know that ‚Äòrace‚Äô is not fair, and polls arguments in the order
they are passed.  Thus, we pass ‚Äòfuture_to_try‚Äô to ‚Äòrace‚Äô first so it
gets a chance to complete even if ‚Äòmax_time‚Äô is a very short duration.
