the ‚Äòfuture_to_try‚Äô succeeded and we get a ‚ÄòLeft(output)‚Äô, we return
‚ÄòOk(output)‚Äô.  If the sleep timer elapsed instead and we get a
‚ÄòRight(())‚Äô, we ignore the ‚Äò()‚Äô with ‚Äò_‚Äô and return ‚ÄòErr(max_time)‚Äô
