convert the string data to bytes.  The ‚Äòwrite_all‚Äô method on ‚Äòstream‚Äô
takes a ‚Äò&[u8]‚Äô and sends those bytes directly down the connection.
Because the ‚Äòwrite_all‚Äô operation could fail, we use ‚Äòunwrap‚Äô on any
error result as before.  Again, in a real application you would add
